sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client (Web Browser)
    participant WebServer as Web Server (C-Logic)
    participant DBServer as Database Server (Storage)

    Note over Client, DBServer: Scenario A: Succesvolle zoekopdracht

    Client->>WebServer: 1: GET /recipe/carbonara
    activate WebServer
    WebServer->>DBServer: 2: SQL SELECT (carbonara)
    activate DBServer
    DBServer-->>WebServer: 3: return Data Found
    deactivate DBServer
    WebServer-->>Client: 4: HTTP 200 OK (HTML Page)
    deactivate WebServer

    Note over Client, DBServer: Scenario B: Niet-succesvolle flow (Recept niet gevonden)

    Client->>WebServer: 5: GET /recipe/onbekend-gerecht
    activate WebServer
    WebServer->>DBServer: 6: SQL SELECT (onbekend-gerecht)
    activate DBServer
    DBServer-->>WebServer: 7: return NULL / Empty Result
    deactivate DBServer
    
    Note right of WebServer: Logic check: Data is leeg. <br/>Genereer foutmelding.
    
    WebServer-->>Client: 8: HTTP 404 Not Found (Error Page)
    deactivate WebServer

    Note over Client: Gebruiker ziet: "Oeps! Recept niet gevonden."